############################################################################
# Magentomodule ProductNavigation 0.1.0 from narf-studios GmbH #############
############################################################################

This module offers a horizontal navigation in the products view to the other
products in this category.
This will be realized over a sitemap-optimizer.xml file which contains following urls:
- categories
- products
- products in different categories
- cms pages

Requirements:
- Magento 1.4.x, 1.5.x, 1.6.x
- Mage_Sitemap module must be enabled
- Narfstudios_Base must be installed and can be found under https://github.com/narf-studios/magento-narfstudios-base

Installation:
- Copy the folder structure into your Magento system
- Create a sitemap folder in your Magento root directory
- Go to Catalog/Google Sitemap in your Adminarea and generate a sitemap in the sitemap/ folder
- Configure the templates if you want to change the look and the position of the navigation

I do not see a navigation. What can I do?
- Check if there is a file called sitemap-optimizer.xml in your sitemap folder
- Check if the navigation templates are configured correctly
